    ENSEMBLE NVT
    STEPS  30
    TIMESTEP 0.5
    TEMPERATURE 300.0
    COMVEL_TOL  2.0E-7
    &SHELL
      TEMPERATURE 25.0
      TEMP_TOL 25.0
    &END
